			"condition": "dt.now.isInRange('12/25', '12/25') && dt.now.getLocalTime().hour >4",
			"prompt": "Let's see. <anim cat='jiboji' filter='santa-scanner, without-santa'/>.<break size='0.5'/> I think he's probably back in the north Pole by now.  ",
